[Libbitcoin](http://libbitcoin.org) is a set of cross platform C++ libraries for building bitcoin applications. The toolkit consists of several libraries, example applications, test suites and end-user applications.

##History
Libbitcoin was announced on July 21, 2011. (2.1) It was created by [[Amir Taaki|Amir_Taaki]] and a community of open source developers. (2.2)

